  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    EU Exit guidance for agri-food stakeholders from Defra
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">The Agri-Food chain stakeholder team at Defra has shared guidance to ensure that businesses are ready for leaving the EU on 31 October</p>

  </div>
</div>

